name: Baby Base
description: Launched on October 26, 2025, Baby Base (BASE) is a meme cryptocurrency built on the Base blockchain. Inspired by Brian Armstrong, the CEO of Coinbase, the project aims to blend humor and community engagement with blockchain transparency. Baby Base features a fixed supply of 21,000,000 tokens and a deflationary model that gradually reduces circulation through manual burns.
